@startuml
title Live Scoring "Hot Path" Sequence

actor Scorer
participant "React Native App\n(Admin)" as AdminApp
participant "Spring Boot\nAPI & Engine" as Backend
database PostgreSQL as DB
database Redis as Cache
participant "Spring Boot\nSSE Emitter" as SSE
actor "Score Viewer" as Viewer
participant "React Native App\n(Viewer)" as ViewerApp

ViewerApp -> SSE : Subscribe to Match Events (SSE)
activate SSE

Scorer -> AdminApp : Input Delivery (e.g., 4 Runs)
AdminApp -> Backend : POST /api/matches/{id}/deliveries
activate Backend

Backend -> Backend : Calculate new state\n(score, strike rotation)
Backend -> DB : INSERT INTO deliveries
Backend -> DB : UPDATE innings & match (if needed)
Backend -> Cache : SET match_{id}_live_state
Backend -> SSE : Publish DeliveryEvent

Backend --> AdminApp : 201 Created
deactivate Backend
AdminApp --> Scorer : UI Confirmation

SSE -> ViewerApp : Event: match_update (JSON payload)
ViewerApp --> Viewer : UI updates score & commentary instantly
deactivate SSE
@enduml
